parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause a loss of braking ability, leading to accidents, property damage, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor without any prior warning

the vehicle has no ability to slow or stop.
